They meta-analyzed the effects of CC on the potential distribution of 1,205 birds using eight Ecological Niche Models (ENM) and three projected climate models (AOGCM). Show the variability of range change estimates between ENMs and AOGCM. Advice for weighting effect sizes by the variability of species estimates due to uncertainty in modeling.},
